import React from 'react';
import { Box, Button, Grid, Paper, Typography, TextField, IconButton } from '@mui/material';
import SearchIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Search';
import { DataGrid } from '@mui/x-data-grid'; // For displaying the client list
import ArrowUpwardIcon from '@mui/icons-material/ArrowUpward';
import ArrowDownwardIcon from '@mui/icons-material/ArrowDownward';

const columns = [
  { field: 'companyName', headerName: 'Company Name', width: 180 },
  { field: 'name', headerName: 'Name', width: 160 },
  { field: 'email', headerName: 'Email Address', width: 220 },
  { field: 'totalOutstanding', headerName: 'Total Outstanding', width: 180 },
  { field: 'note', headerName: 'Note', width: 220 },
];

const rows = [
  { id: 1, companyName: 'Amazon', name: 'Eleanor Pena', email: 'finance@amazon.com', totalOutstanding: '$32,235', note: 'Authorization Created' },
  { id: 2, companyName: 'Apple', name: 'Miles, Esther', email: 'support@apple.com', totalOutstanding: '$17,000', note: 'Appeal Note' },
  { id: 3, companyName: 'Mailchimp', name: 'Henry, Arthur', email: 'finance@mailchimp.com', totalOutstanding: '$46,000', note: 'Authorization' },
  { id: 4, companyName: 'Evernote', name: 'Black, Marvin', email: 'support@evernote.com', totalOutstanding: '$32,235', note: 'Attach Clinical' },
  { id: 5, companyName: 'Spotify', name: 'Nguyen, Shane', email: 'support@spotify.com', totalOutstanding: '$12,000', note: 'Admission Advisor' },
  { id: 6, companyName: 'Amazon', name: 'Nguyen, Shane', email: 'finance@amazon.com', totalOutstanding: '$57,000', note: 'Web Authorization' },
];

export default function Dashboard() {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ padding: '20px' }}>
      <Grid container spacing={3}>
        {/* Statistics Cards */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
          <Paper sx={{ padding: '20px', backgroundColor: '#fff', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', justifyContent: 'space-between', height: '200px' }}>
            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: '#4caf50' }}>
              Total Outstanding
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ color: '#4caf50' }}>
              $15,420
            </Typography>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center' }}>
              <ArrowUpwardIcon sx={{ color: '#4caf50' }} />
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#4caf50' }}>
                2.3% Last month
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
          <Paper sx={{ padding: '20px', backgroundColor: '#fff', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', justifyContent: 'space-between', height: '200px' }}>
            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: '#f44336' }}>
              Overdue
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ color: '#f44336' }}>
              $6,140
            </Typography>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center' }}>
              <ArrowDownwardIcon sx={{ color: '#f44336' }} />
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#f44336' }}>
                2.3% Last month
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
          <Paper sx={{ padding: '20px', backgroundColor: '#fff', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', justifyContent: 'space-between', height: '200px' }}>
            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: '#2196f3' }}>
              In Draft
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ color: '#2196f3' }}>
              $5,425
            </Typography>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center' }}>
              <ArrowUpwardIcon sx={{ color: '#2196f3' }} />
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#2196f3' }}>
                1.8% Last month
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>

      {/* New Client Button */}
      <Button
        sx={{
          backgroundColor: '#f44336',
          color: 'white',
          textTransform: 'none',
          padding: '8px 16px',
          borderRadius: '4px',
          "&:hover": {
            backgroundColor: '#d32f2f',
          },
        }}
        startIcon={<SearchIcon />}
      >
        New Client +
      </Button>

      {/* Client List Table */}
      <Box sx={{ marginTop: '30px' }}>
        <Grid container spacing={2}>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Paper sx={{ width: '100%', overflow: 'hidden' }}>
              <DataGrid rows={rows} columns={columns} pageSize={5} rowsPerPageOptions={[5]} />
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
}
